\frametitle{9. Functions (cont'd)}
Define function:\\
{\small
\begin{Verbatim}[commandchars=\\\[\]]
myfunction <- function(arg1, opt2=2, ...){

 \fbox[\blue[functionbody] ]

 return(...)
}
\end{Verbatim}
}
Use the function:
{\small
\begin{verbatim}
myfunction(1, 2)  myfunction(1, opt2=2)  myfunction(1)
\end{verbatim}
}
